      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "莫要怕，我知道不是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "明明是他……明明是他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "二姐……小弟……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "我不知道……我不知道……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "我没有偷瞧……我没有偷瞧……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "text": "我……我的血也……也是臭的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "我的血香……好香……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "真的香，不信你闻闻，好香……好香……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "果然很香……香的更好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "你们还要我来动手么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "灵铃！我的女儿，我的乖女儿，这臭男人说的不错，妈自从你走了后，便已疯了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "text": "水……水灵光真是她女儿？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "不是，只是想女儿想得疯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "毒？谁敢在我女儿身上下毒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "这……唉！不说也罢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "你说不说？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "放屁，你只管说出就是。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zhuang_li_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宫装丽人",
      "text": "放屁放屁！快说快说！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "text": "飧毒大师……",
      "tone": "无奈",
